	ment games with trained tutors.\, Snacks are provided at every Homework He
	lp: Thanks to the donors of\n\nThe Seattle Public Library Foundation\n\nfo
	r sponsoring this event.\n\nEvent Logistics:\n\n\, Registration is not req
	uired but these programs are very popular and the room capacity can fill u
	p quickly.\, While Homework Help is available to students from kindergarte
